en.name: 6.8x51mm SIG Venari SP
en.description: The Sig Sauer Venari Soft Point ammunition is a high-performance hunting round designed for the .277 Sig Fury cartridge. This traditional soft-point hunting ammunition features a 130-grain soft-point bullet loaded into reloadable brass cases. With a muzzle velocity of 2710 fps and muzzle energy of 2120 ft-lbs, it delivers excellent terminal performance on deer-sized and big game animals. The Venari line combines SIG SAUER's renowned quality with the versatility needed for various hunting scenarios, making it an ideal choice for hunters seeking reliable and effective ammunition for their .277 Sig Fury rifles.
